<h1 class="display-4 text-center mt-5">Santarosa Motorworks, Inc.</h1>
<p class="h6 fw-normal text-center mt-2">
    Santarosa Motor Works, Inc. is a bus and truck body manufacturer, which started operation last October 2, 1987 is composed of 100% Filipino Stockholders 
    whose primary aim is to produce quality trucks and bus mounted on Nissan Diesel chassis and MAN chassis supplied by Columbian Motors Corporation. 
    A flexibility which are purposely applicable for city and provincial operations. But recently, after Daewoo Philippines closed shop, 
    Santarosa has now take over the spare parts for new Daewoo Buses. Galleries below are some of its notable bus models.
</p>

